subSections.title: Glyph origin
subSections.text:
Compound of [[木]] and [[勝]]. 勝 replaces the reading [[かち]] (''kachi''), from the wood name [[かちのき]] (''kachinoki'').

It is also called [[ぬるで]] (''nurude''), after contracted ぬで (''nude'').
